'''二(2-吡啶基)甲烷'''是一种有机化合物，化学式为C<sub>11</sub>H<sub>10</sub>N<sub>2</sub>，它可用作配体和金属形成[[配合物|配合物]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Dalton Transactions|volume=44|issue=41|language=en|issn=1477-9226|date=2015|pages=18247–18259|doi=10.1039/C5DT02830B|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C5DT02830B|title=Group 13 complexes of dipyridylmethane, a forgotten ligand in coordination chemistry|accessdate=2020-11-25|author=Petra Vasko, Virva Kinnunen, Jani O. Moilanen, Tracey L. Roemmele, René T. Boeré, Jari Konu, Heikki M. Tuononen}}</ref>

==合成==
将[[2-甲基吡啶|2-甲基吡啶]]溶于干燥的[[四氢呋喃|四氢呋喃]]，降温至−78 °C，逐滴加入[[正丁基锂|正丁基锂]]，升温至−20 °C后加入[[2-氟吡啶|2-氟吡啶]]，加入冰块水解，经提纯后得到产物二(2-吡啶基)甲烷。<ref name=Golden>{{cite journal|journal=The Journal of Organic Chemistry|volume=82|issue=14|language=en|issn=0022-3263|date=2017-07-21|pages=7215–7222|doi=10.1021/acs.joc.7b00786|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.joc.7b00786|title=Boron Dipyridylmethene (DIPYR) Dyes: Shedding Light on Pyridine-Based Chromophores|accessdate=2020-11-25|author=Jessica H. Golden, John W. Facendola, Daniel Sylvinson M. R., Cecilia Quintana Baez, Peter I. Djurovich, Mark E. Thompson}}</ref>

